description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=3/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=0/3. You are a worthless rabbit. However you have the privilege of helping further science. What lies before you are a series of experiments. They will test you speed, your agility and the effects of high powered lasers on rabbits. Why you may ask? SCIENCE!
